procstep.procdesc: Corrected Ash Street Station Boundary per The Rockland County Department of Environmental Resources.
Updated park boundaries based on offical tax parcels created by J.W.Sewall dated February 2009.
Added Collins Property per A. Beers on 2/2010. It is joint ownership with the State, but Allan wanted it in our file (as other joint properties are!)
Added 3 parcels to Buttermilk Falls Park per Mike Dimola, According to the survey done in 1995 these are part of the park (approximately 2 acres total): 65.11-1-42 65.11-1-41 65.11-1-24

Added 2 parcels to existing county parks, per allan beers, 3/1/2010: 1. 43.19-1-1, 0.4 acres (Annie's Nails) added to Dutch Garden 2. 39.46-1-1, 93 acres, Ramapo Land Co., added to Wrightmans Plateau. NOTE: this park is jointly owned by the State and the County. Per Allan Beers, he wants it in the County shapefile
